OL,6,FA 71-year-old man who murdered his
OL,7,Fwife at their home has been jailed.
OL,9,Fto killing Denise Steeves, 59, at
OL,10,Ftheir home in Diamond Meadow Lodge
OL,11,FPark, on Weston Road in Brean, .
OL,13,FBristol Crown Court heard how Steeves
OL,14,Fstabbed his wife on 25 October 2023,
OL,15,Fand then called 999 after the attack
OL,16,Fto tell police he had murdered her.
OL,18,FWhen police arrived at the couple's
OL,19,Fhome, they arrested him and provided
OL,20,FMs Steeves with CPR. She died at the
OL,21,Fscene.
