OL,6,FSteeves was charged the following day.
OL,8,FDuring a hearing at Bristol Crown
OL,9,FCourt on Thursday 29 February, Steeves
OL,10,Fwas jailed for life with a minimum
OL,11,Fterm of 14 years and two months.
OL,13,FHis sentence was then reduced to 13
OL,14,Fyears and 300 days due to the time he
OL,15,Fhad already served on remand after his
OL,16,Farrest.
