OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentence, Senior
OL,7,FInvestigating Officer Detective
OL,8,FInspector Neil Meade from the Major
OL,9,FCrime Investigation Team said: "I want
OL,10,Fto express my heartfelt condolences to
OL,11,FDenise's family and loved ones after
OL,12,Fshe was so suddenly taken away from
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"Steeves admitted in interview to
OL,16,Ffatally stabbing his wife, but said he
OL,17,Fhad no recollection of picking up the
OL,18,Fknife.
